---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Adozioni a distanza"
  description="Adotta un bambino a distanza con la Chiesa Cristiana Efraim. Garantisci istruzione, nutrizione e cure mediche a un bambino in Kenya o India."
>
  <!-- Section 1: Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-slate-dark overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/images/uploads/gruppo-bambini-volontari.jpg" alt="Gruppo di bambini e volontari della missione" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-slate-dark/90 via-slate-dark/75 to-slate-dark/60"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-28 md:py-36">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-block text-accent font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Cambia una vita</span>
        <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">
          Adotta un bambino a distanza
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg font-serif italic text-white/70 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          L'adozione di un bambino non cambierà il mondo; ma per quel bambino, il mondo cambierà.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 2: Cos'è l'adozione a distanza -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-warm">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
        <!-- Left: narrative text -->
        <div>
          <span class="inline-block text-accent-dark font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Cos'è l'adozione a distanza</span>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text mb-6">Un legame che cambia tutto</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              Adottare un bambino a distanza non significa acquistare un servizio. Significa scegliere di camminare accanto a un bambino nel suo percorso di crescita, diventando una presenza concreta nella sua vita. È un legame reale, fatto di lettere, foto, aggiornamenti e della consapevolezza che qualcuno, dall'altra parte del mondo, crede in lui.
            </p>
            <p>
              Il tuo sostegno garantisce a quel bambino ciò che ogni bambino merita: cibo ogni giorno, la possibilità di andare a scuola, cure mediche quando ne ha bisogno e un luogo sicuro dove crescere. Non è solo un aiuto economico: è la certezza, per quel bambino, di non essere solo.
            </p>
            <p>
              Ogni bambino ha il diritto di sognare. Con la tua adozione, quel sogno diventa possibile.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: photo -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-md">
          <img src="/images/uploads/bambini-nutrizione-1.jpg" alt="Bambini sostenuti dalla missione" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 3: Come funziona -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-cream">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <span class="inline-block text-accent-dark font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Tre semplici passi</span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text">Come funziona</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-divider/50 p-8 text-center relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-dark text-white text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">1</div>
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-accent/15 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent-dark" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">Contattaci</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Scrivici e ti assegneremo un bambino in base alle esigenze più urgenti.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-divider/50 p-8 text-center relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-dark text-white text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">2</div>
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-accent/15 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent-dark" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">Ricevi la scheda</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Entro 15 giorni ricevi via email la scheda con foto, nome e dati personali del bambino.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-divider/50 p-8 text-center relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-3 -left-3 w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-primary-dark text-white text-sm font-bold flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">3</div>
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-accent/15 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-5">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-accent-dark" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 14c1.49-1.46 3-3.21 3-5.5A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 16.5 3c-1.76 0-3 .5-4.5 2-1.5-1.5-2.74-2-4.5-2A5.5 5.5 0 0 0 2 8.5c0 2.3 1.5 4.05 3 5.5l7 7Z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-text mb-3">Sostieni ogni mese</h3>
          <p class="text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">Il tuo contributo mensile garantisce scuola, cibo e cure mediche al bambino.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 4: Cosa include il tuo sostegno -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-warm">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-accent-dark font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Il tuo contributo</span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text">Cosa include il tuo sostegno</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-divider/50 p-8 md:p-10">
          <ul class="space-y-4">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/></svg>
              <span class="text-text-secondary">Frequenza scolastica e materiale didattico</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/></svg>
              <span class="text-text-secondary">Pasti quotidiani e nutrizione adeguata</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/></svg>
              <span class="text-text-secondary">Cure mediche e visite periodiche</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/></svg>
              <span class="text-text-secondary">Divisa scolastica e abbigliamento</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/></svg>
              <span class="text-text-secondary">Attività ricreative e formazione spirituale</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-primary" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><path d="m9 11 3 3L22 4"/></svg>
              <span class="text-text-secondary">Aggiornamenti periodici con foto del bambino</span>
            </li>
          </ul>

          <!-- Subtle note -->
          <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl bg-primary/5 p-5">
            <p class="text-text-secondary text-sm leading-relaxed text-center">
              Il contributo parte da <strong class="text-text">35&euro; al mese</strong>. Contattaci per trovare insieme la formula più adatta a te.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- CTA button -->
        <div class="mt-8 text-center">
          <a
            href="mailto:info@missionekenya.com?subject=Adozione%20a%20distanza%20-%20Richiesta%20informazioni"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-primary px-8 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white shadow-md hover:bg-primary-dark hover:shadow-lg transition-all"
          >
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
            Scrivici per adottare
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 5: Scrivi al tuo bambino -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-cream">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-accent-dark font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Lettere e messaggi</span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text">Resta in contatto</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <!-- Left: description -->
        <div class="space-y-4 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            Puoi scrivere lettere o email al bambino che sostieni. Le lettere vanno scritte in inglese: le consegneremo personalmente al bambino durante le nostre visite alla missione.
          </p>
          <p>
            Riceverai anche le risposte del bambino, i suoi disegni e aggiornamenti sul suo percorso di crescita. È un modo speciale per costruire un legame autentico nonostante la distanza.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: email card -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-sm border border-divider/50 p-8">
          <label class="block text-sm font-medium text-text-secondary uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Scrivi a</label>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-cream rounded-xl p-4 border border-divider/50 mb-4">
            <code id="adoption-email" class="flex-1 text-lg font-mono font-semibold text-primary-dark break-all">
              info@missionekenya.com
            </code>
            <button
              id="copy-adoption-email"
              type="button"
              class="shrink-0 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg bg-primary px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-primary-dark transition-colors"
              aria-label="Copia email adozioni negli appunti"
            >
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="14" height="14" x="8" y="8" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2"/></svg>
              <span id="copy-adoption-label">Copia</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
            Scrivi in inglese, consegneremo la lettera al bambino e ti invieremo la sua risposta.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 6: FAQ adozioni -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-warm">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
          <span class="inline-block text-accent-dark font-medium text-sm tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">Domande frequenti</span>
          <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-text">Hai delle domande?</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-divider/50 overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 cursor-pointer list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-text">Quanto dura l'adozione a distanza?</h3>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              <p>L'adozione prosegue fino al raggiungimento della maggiore età del bambino. Puoi interrompere il sostegno in qualsiasi momento contattandoci.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-divider/50 overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 cursor-pointer list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-text">Posso scegliere il bambino da adottare?</h3>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              <p>Ti assegneremo il bambino con le esigenze più urgenti. Riceverai la sua scheda completa con foto e dati personali entro 15 giorni.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-divider/50 overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 cursor-pointer list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-text">Come ricevo gli aggiornamenti?</h3>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              <p>Riceverai aggiornamenti periodici via email sul bambino adottato, incluse foto e notizie sul suo percorso scolastico e di crescita.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-divider/50 overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 cursor-pointer list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-text">Posso incontrare il bambino?</h3>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              <p>Sì, organizziamo periodicamente viaggi missionari in Kenya e India. Contattaci per sapere le prossime date disponibili.</p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="group bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-divider/50 overflow-hidden">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4 p-6 cursor-pointer list-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
              <h3 class="font-serif text-lg font-semibold text-text">Il sostegno è deducibile fiscalmente?</h3>
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="shrink-0 text-text-secondary group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" aria-hidden="true"><path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-6 text-text-secondary leading-relaxed">
              <p>Sì, le donazioni al Centro Cristiano Efraim Onlus sono deducibili/detraibili secondo la normativa vigente.</p>
            </div>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Section 7: CTA -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-dark">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ogni bambino merita un futuro</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/70 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Inizia oggi. Il tuo sostegno fa la differenza.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a
          href="mailto:info@missionekenya.com?subject=Adozione%20a%20distanza%20-%20Richiesta%20informazioni"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-accent px-8 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-dark shadow-md hover:bg-accent-dark hover:text-white transition-all"
        >
          Scrivici per adottare
        </a>
        <a
          href="/missioni/"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border-2 border-white/30 px-8 py-3 text-base font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white/10 transition-all"
        >
          Scopri le missioni
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  function setupCopyButton(buttonId: string, codeId: string) {
    const button = document.getElementById(buttonId);
    const code = document.getElementById(codeId);
    if (!button || !code) return;

    button.addEventListener('click', async () => {
      const text = code.textContent?.trim() || '';
      try {
        await navigator.clipboard.writeText(text);
        const label = button.querySelector('span');
        const originalText = label?.textContent;
        if (label) {
          label.textContent = 'Copiato!';
          setTimeout(() => {
            label.textContent = originalText || 'Copia';
          }, 2000);
        }
      } catch {
        const textarea = document.createElement('textarea');
        textarea.value = text;
        textarea.style.position = 'fixed';
        textarea.style.opacity = '0';
        document.body.appendChild(textarea);
        textarea.select();
        document.execCommand('copy');
        document.body.removeChild(textarea);
      }
    });
  }

  setupCopyButton('copy-adoption-email', 'adoption-email');
</script>
